title: Thom Hartmann Program - October 31 2013
description:
October 31, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 

Hour One: About that $700 million missing from Medicare - Wendell Potter, Deadly Spin / Plus, An ObamaCare cooperative success story - Eliot Richardson, Chicago Small Business Advocacy Council

Hour Two: Humankinds Most Dangerous Moment?  Kevin Kamps, Beyond Nuclear / Plus, Transforming kids at Hunter School - Ryan Barber, The Hunter School

Hour Three: Big Corps vs. Big Govt - Peter Schweizer, EXTORTION: How Politicians Extract Your Money, Buy Votes, and Line Their Own Pockets
